## Podcasts

**Marketing School — Neil Patel & Eric Siu**
- URL: https://marketingschool.io
- Why relevant: Daily podcast covering SEO, AI content 
  tools, and growth tactics. Short episodes (5-10 mins) 
  make it easy to track trends. Eric Siu is on this 
  expert list, making this a direct extension of his 
  content.

**Search Off the Record — Google Search Team**
- URL: https://podcasts.google.com (search "Search Off 
  the Record")
- Why relevant: Official podcast from Google's Search 
  Relations team. Directly addresses how Google evaluates 
  AI-generated content, helpful content updates, and 
  quality signals — essential context for any AI SEO 
  content strategy.

**Leveling Up — Eric Siu**
- URL: https://www.youtube.com/@LevelingUpOfficial
- Why relevant: Covers agentic SEO workflows, 
  programmatic content systems, and AI-assisted growth 
  at scale. Eric Siu is on this expert list.

**The Recipe for SEO Success — Kate Toon**
- URL: https://kateslingsby.com/podcast
- Why relevant: Practical SEO podcast that has dedicated 
  significant coverage to AI content production, quality 
  thresholds, and how to use AI without triggering 
  Google penalties.

