## Newsletters

**SEOFOMO — Aleyda Solis**
- URL: https://seofomo.co
- Why relevant: Weekly newsletter covering the latest in 
  SEO and AI search. Aleyda Solis is on this expert list. 
  35,000+ subscribers. Highly curated — every issue 
  contains signal, not noise.

**Growth Memo — Kevin Indig**
- URL: https://www.kevin-indig.com/newsletter
- Why relevant: Kevin Indig is on this expert list. 
  Deep-dive essays on SEO strategy, AI's impact on 
  search, and content at scale. One of the most 
  analytically rigorous newsletters in the space.

**SparkToro Weekly — Rand Fishkin & Amanda Natividad**
- URL: https://sparktoro.com/blog
- Why relevant: Rand Fishkin is on this expert list. 
  Covers audience research, zero-click search, and AI's 
  impact on how content gets discovered — directly 
  relevant to AI SEO content strategy.

**The Savvy SEO — Connor Gillivan**
- URL: https://connorgillivan.com/newsletter
- Why relevant: Connor Gillivan is on this expert list. 
  Weekly newsletter with practical SEO workflows, AI 
  content processes, and B2B SEO case studies.

